  <summary>12/11/2007--Passed House amended.
Expresses sympathy for the victims of Cyclone Sidr which has affected southern Bangladesh. Urges the U.S. government to make available all appropriate assistance requested by the Bangladeshi authorities. Reaffirms the House of Representatives' commitment to provide relief aid as the cyclone's effects continue to unfold.</summary>
